{"TopicId":91463,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Bad Suggestions for KSP","CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T12:38:29Z","PageNum":4,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T03:17:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemove all screen resolution options. Fullscreen only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T11:57:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd Kerbal snacks -- but they expire after three kerbin-days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UnionPacific1983WP","CreatedById":140982,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T13:25:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake every non-demo part DLC that you have to pay for individually for each part every day. Oh, and there\u0027s no reminder and/or\u00A0countdown to when any part\u0027s pay timer may run out.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-26T13:26:12Z\u0022 title=\u002209/26/2016 01:26  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by UnionPacific1983WP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TopHeavy11","CreatedById":154744,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T14:37:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAmp up stock heating by 99999999%!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T14:42:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222774438\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474859835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemove all screen resolution options. Fullscreen only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...at 800x600.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T15:08:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222774438\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474859835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemove all screen resolution options. Fullscreen only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222774985\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474900960\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...at 800x600.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd in the old black and green pixelated high contrast screen colors so that KSP resembles this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image_a661e8c2-8e59-402e-a690-cfe2999c9c\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.hanselman.com/blog/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/ab918f8d45a6_9B4E/image_a661e8c2-8e59-402e-a690-cfe2999c9c96.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(This is a screen shot I found online of the old game, Oregon Trail...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T15:52:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00221569922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221417997145\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129900\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022natonator200\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/7/2014 at 7:05 PM, natonator200 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhave the loading screen pic turn into \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EYOUR COMPUTER SUCKS!!!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E if it takes more than a minute to load.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as I can still play KSP, I\u0027d like that, because, it would definitely happen to me \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T15:58:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDelete all the engines except the Puff\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T16:09:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake all new rocket parts to replace the stock parts. They all look like and have the same specifications of the ACME rocket parts used by Wile E. Coyote. For reference:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Upt7ZTvcriY?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NFUN","CreatedById":78715,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T16:47:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222775016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474902518\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(This is a screen shot I found online of the old game, Oregon Trail...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClearly. Somebody died of dysentery!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe green should be #BADA56, btw. One off from Badass.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T22:21:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd a system where Kerbals get less happy with other Kerbals depending on how long it has been since they showered. At some point, Kerbals will rather throw themselves out the airlock rather than deal with Bill\u0027s BO.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-26T22:22:03Z\u0022 title=\u002209/26/2016 10:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by njmksr\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceplaneAddict","CreatedById":149322,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T22:25:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReverse the atmospheric pressure curves for all planets, so close to ground it\u0027s a vacuum, and higher up, it\u0027s thick. Real thick.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T00:58:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPort KSP to N64.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Firemetal","CreatedById":164725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T02:06:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAllow Danny2462 to make any changes he wants to. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V7 Aerospace","CreatedById":156062,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T16:48:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222775776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474937897\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPort KSP to N64.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBanjo KSPzooie!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T19:30:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222776560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474994920\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156062\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V7 Aerospace\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, V7 Aerospace said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBanjo KSPzooie!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuper Kerbal 64!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T21:34:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222776813\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475004621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuper Kerbal 64!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConKerb\u0027s Bad Fur Day!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMarioKerb 64!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe that CommNet should be overhauled to only work via walkie-talkies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T00:30:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP-themed Magic-style trading card game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T01:20:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScrap the game and turn it into a mod for besiege!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T01:24:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd guns to the game; make it so that you can get into orbit by going straight up; remove Eve and Tylo because they\u0027re too difficult for new players.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T12:56:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake KSP incompatible with ts previous version mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222775016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474902518\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 26.09.2016 at 6:08 PM, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd in the old black and green pixelated high contrast screen colors so that KSP resembles this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIsn\u0027t it a thread for bad suggestions?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis looks wonderful! A nostalgic dream!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"55delta","CreatedById":101735,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T19:16:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving KSP require the player to submit a complete flight-plan before allowing a vessel to fly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T19:27:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475090205\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022101735\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u002255delta\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, 55delta said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving KSP require the player to submit a complete flight-plan before allowing a vessel to fly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is plain evil. Or maybe plane evil. But evil for sure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKosanianMethod","CreatedById":163034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T19:41:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want weather implemented. High winds, muddy dirt is hard to land on, the runway becomes slick when it rains.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, there should be an aircraft carrier complete with elevators, arrestor wires,\u00A0catapults, and 6,000 Kebals.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake Kerbals hold guns to shoot each other, too, with real-life gun models and bullet physics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T19:58:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave gravity drop off linearly, instead of the inverse square of distance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}